00E016  2               ; Optimum compression would reduce these 65536 bytes by 0 percent
00E016  2               
00E016  2               ; Chi square distribution for 65536 samples is 232.01, and
00E016  2               ; randomly would exceed this value 75.00 percent of the time
00E016  2               
00E016  2               ; Arithmetic mean value of data bytes is 127.6724, 127.5 would be random
00E016  2               ; Monte Carlo value for Pi is 3.122871269, error 0.60 percent
