00ED8C  2               
00ED8C  2               LAB_COPPER
00ED8C  2  20 C2 00           JSR   LAB_GBYT          ; peek next byte
00ED8F  2  C9 A2              CMP   #TK_CLEAR
00ED91  2  F0 17              BEQ   @c_clear
