00EDFA  2  20 EC D7           JSR   LAB_GTWRD         ; x (16-bit) → FAC1_3(lo), FAC1_2(hi)
00EDFD  2  A5 AF              LDA   FAC1_3
00EDFF  2  8D 11 A0           STA   VGC_P0             ; x low
00EE02  2  A5 AE              LDA   FAC1_2
